source.name: Test Map
source.description: Data providing the location, type and capacity of public and private community facilities in the Bronx, including schools, parks, libraries, public safety, day care, foster care, special needs housing, health and mental health facilities and programs. Refer to attached SelFac_datainfo.pdf for facility type designation and definitions.
